28:31.001 --> 28:33.796
I mean, there's very little
that can be done

28:33.879 --> 28:37.466
because of, you know, politics
and everything else,

28:37.550 --> 28:41.387
whereas I, as, like, an individual,

28:41.470 --> 28:44.932
actually had some power
to contribute to change here.

28:45.015 --> 28:46.600
¡Hola!

