29:07.204 --> 29:09.165
Nowadays, I don't see you anymore.

29:09.248 --> 29:10.749
What's happening in your life?

29:10.833 --> 29:12.293
I have to travel frequently
to the States now

29:12.376 --> 29:14.837
because I just have one year left
to finish my doctorate.

29:14.920 --> 29:17.506
And they're like,
"Samantha, you have to write,

29:17.590 --> 29:19.925
you can't spend all your time in Peru."

29:20.009 --> 29:22.261
(laughter)

29:22.344 --> 29:25.556
I've got my PhD
that I'm trying to finish this year,

29:25.639 --> 29:29.518
