29:46.076 --> 29:47.453
SAMANTHA:
Oh.

29:49.830 --> 29:51.874
-HARRY: Four seconds.
-(laughter)

29:53.876 --> 29:55.878
(laughing)

29:55.961 --> 29:57.963
