31:01.485 --> 31:03.779
HARRY:
Look what I've got you.

31:03.862 --> 31:05.155
Hey, this.

31:05.239 --> 31:07.032
This.

31:07.116 --> 31:09.326
This is good food, good protein.

31:10.411 --> 31:12.413
(growling softly)

31:13.581 --> 31:15.249
He's getting big.

31:15.332 --> 31:16.792
He's getting beautiful.

31:16.875 --> 31:19.503
And, uh, yeah,
hopefully in the next month or so,

31:19.587 --> 31:21.171
I'm gonna start taking him out

31:21.255 --> 31:23.757
so he can start eating
outside the enclosure

31:23.841 --> 31:26.051
and, uh, catch some cool animals.

31:27.511 --> 31:31.181
I'm gonna teach you
how to become a killer.

31:32.433 --> 31:34.059
Okay?

31:38.522 --> 31:40.149
(snake hisses)

31:40.232 --> 31:43.027
Amazon tree boa.

31:43.110 --> 31:45.946
Remember this. Common snake.

31:46.030 --> 31:47.948
This is the snake.

31:48.032 --> 31:50.284
You see it? You smell it?

31:50.367 --> 31:52.244
I've got it.

31:52.328 --> 31:54.496
Look here.

31:54.580 --> 31:56.415
This insect here.

31:56.498 --> 31:58.250
Here. (chuckles)

31:58.334 --> 31:59.501
Look.

31:59.585 --> 32:01.962
There's a frog right there.

32:02.046 --> 32:04.298
Frog, right there.

32:04.381 --> 32:06.175
(laughs)

32:06.258 --> 32:08.260
♪ ♪

