about hanging himself

1:21:01.774 --> 1:21:05.611
and, uh, taking, like,
all the pills that he could find

1:21:05.695 --> 1:21:09.031
basically in-in the platform
where he stays.

1:21:09.115 --> 1:21:13.452
And he hasn't really... he isn't...
he hasn't talked like that for many years.

1:21:13.536 --> 1:21:15.830
So, um...

1:21:15.913 --> 1:21:19.375
If he's cutting himself
and talking about killing himself,

1:21:19.458 --> 1:21:22.503
he needs somebody to supervise him.

1:21:22.587 --> 1:21:27.174
You need to go and talk to him
and lay down some boundaries.

1:21:27.258 --> 1:21:30.928
I mean, he's putting you through
some emotional trauma as well

1:21:31.012 --> 1:21:32.930
by not getting help.

1:21:34.015 --> 1:21:36.017
And that's not fair to you.

1:21:38.561 --> 1:21:39.937
Yeah.

1:21:40.938 --> 1:21:43.816
I don't know the logistics
behind getting him out of there,

1:21:43.899 --> 1:21:45.359
but at the end of the day,

1:21:45.443 --> 1:21:48.279
you don't want to support him
continuing this behavior.

1:21:48.362 --> 1:21:50.781
You want to support him getting help.

1:21:51.782 --> 1:21:53.784
♪ ♪

1:21:57.038 --> 1:22:00.291
NIERY:
Right now he has lots of problems,

1:22:00.374 --> 1:22:03.669
internal conflicts deep within himself

1:22:03.753 --> 1:22:06.380
that he doesn't want to talk about
with anyone.

1:22:06.464 --> 1:22:09.133
It's possible that,

1:22:09.216 --> 1:22:13.804
if he doesn't agree to leave
in the next few weeks,

1:22:13.888 --> 1:22:17.433
I'll have to tell him, as his friend,

1:22:17.516 --> 1:22:21.395
but also as the person in charge
of this project,

1:22:21.479 --> 1:22:25.650
that he has to leave
because he is not mentally stable.

1:22:26.609 --> 1:22:28.361
HARRY:
No, I'm not fucking doing that,

1:22:28.444 --> 1:22:31.906
because Keanu is more important
than fucking anything

1:22:31.989 --> 1:22:34.033
that I have ever fucking done!

1:22:35.910 --> 1:22:37.912
-Fucking stupid.
-(object clatters)

1:22:39.497 --> 1:22:41.499
Fucking stupid.

1:22:43.751 --> 1:22:46.128
SAMANTHA:
He was basically like, "I don't know why

1:22:46.212 --> 1:22:47.963
"you would call that hotline.

1:22:48.047 --> 1:22:49.757
"It's not a big deal.

1:22:49.840 --> 1:22:52.468
"Maybe it was good for you
and it's what you needed to do,

1:22:52.551 --> 1:22:54.595
"but I wish you never would have told me,

1:22:54.679 --> 1:22:57.723
because all it's made me
is more upset and angry."

1:22:57.807 --> 1:23:00.559
And he doesn't think that...

1:23:00.643 --> 1:23:02.228
He knows he has a problem,

1:23:02.311 --> 1:23:05.439
but he's not willing to do anything
about it right now.

1:23:05.523 --> 1:23:09.443
And that he's not ready to leave
and no one can make him leave.

1:23:09.527 --> 1:23:12.196
-(clattering)
-HARRY: I only said one thing.

1:23:12.279 --> 1:23:15.366
SAMANTHA: No, you fought about one thing.
You caused a fight over one stupid thing.

1:23:15.449 --> 1:23:17.118
(Harry muttering)

1:23:17.201 --> 1:23:19.203
-One fucking thing!
-(clattering continues)

1:23:19.286 --> 1:23:20.746
SAMANTHA:
Stop ruining shit.

1:23:20.830 --> 1:23:22.748
HARRY:
I can ruin whatever the fuck I want.

1:23:22.832 --> 1:23:24.542
SAMANTHA:
No, you can't.

1:23:24.625 --> 1:23:26.544
You can't ruin whatever the fuck you want.

1:23:31.924 --> 1:23:34.510
He is the most important fucking thing
to me right now.

1:23:34.593 --> 1:23:36.637
You know, if he fucking dies right now,

1:23:36.721 --> 1:23:40.516
if he goes off and I never see him again,
you know how that's going to affect me?

1:23:40.599 --> 1:23:42.393
I already lost one.

1:23:43.561 --> 1:23:46.063
(crying):
Right?

1:23:46.147 --> 1:23:47.648
So did I.

1:23:47.732 --> 1:23:49.483
You never fucking saw it.

1:23:49.567 --> 1:23:52.528
You only heard it through my voice
and through my tears.

1:23:52.611 --> 1:23:54.905
And you don't think that was enough?

1:23:54.989 --> 1:23:58.075
I don't think you know
how hard it hurt me.

1:24:00.161 --> 1:24:05.040
Everything that I'd ever fucking thought
I'd got back, and I lost it all again.

1:24:06.584 --> 1:24:08.377
I lost that huge chunk of me

1:24:08.461 --> 1:24:11.464
when I was in the military
and I saw all them dead children.

1:24:11.547 --> 1:24:14.592
I saw that fucking poor girl
get slaughtered in front of me.

1:24:14.675 --> 1:24:18.554
And I come here, and I miraculously find
something that makes me fucking happy--

1:24:18.637 --> 1:24:22.850
you, the jungle,
the two things that make me happy--

1:24:22.933 --> 1:24:24.935
and I am lost right now.

1:24:25.019 --> 1:24:28.898
I thought... I thought that I had a friend
in the jungle, and I don't.

1:24:29.940 --> 1:24:31.567
'Cause you...

1:24:33.068 --> 1:24:35.154
...you don't want me here anymore.

1:24:36.238 --> 1:24:38.282
You said, if Keanu wasn't here,

1:24:38.365 --> 1:24:40.868
I'd have gone
and you'd have got on with your life.

1:24:42.703 --> 1:24:45.664
When people treat me like shit
and with disrespect, like you have,

1:24:45.748 --> 1:24:49.168
I don't feel like I want to be here
and I don't feel like I'm your friend.

1:24:49.251 --> 1:24:51.670
And I haven't felt like you're my friend.

1:24:58.886 --> 1:25:01.472
I'm tired of feeling
the way I feel around you.

1:25:03.766 --> 1:25:05.768
SAMANTHA:
Yeah, well, that makes two of us.

1:25:07.561 --> 1:25:09.563
♪ ♪

1:25:24.411 --> 1:25:26.789
HARRY:
Everything I do hurts her.

1:25:26.872 --> 1:25:29.166
Everything she does hurts me.

1:25:33.337 --> 1:25:36.507
SAMANTHA: I feel like everything
that we have to say to each other

1:25:36.590 --> 1:25:40.302
is just to, like, blame or hurt
the other person.

1:25:40.386 --> 1:25:43.180
And, like, the things that I have to say
to him at this moment

1:25:43.264 --> 1:25:47.393
aren't things that would help,
so I just keep them to myself.

1:25:53.274 --> 1:25:58.445
HARRY: We've been on the same road for
a long time, and it's been a bumpy road.

1:25:58.529 --> 1:26:01.949
And now I just want to turn left,
and I just want her to turn right.

1:26:04.785 --> 1:26:06.453
(purring)

1:26:06.537 --> 1:26:09.582
SAMANTHA: With Harry, I just felt like
I was constantly trying to either save him

1:26:09.665 --> 1:26:11.667
or save our relationship.

1:26:11.750 --> 1:26:13.586
(indistinct chatter, laughter)

1:26:14.670 --> 1:26:16.255
And that's not healthy.

1:26:16.338 --> 1:26:18.299
-Oh, no! Oh, my God.
-(laughter)

1:26:20.801 --> 1:26:23.012
(insects buzzing and trilling)

1:26:23.095 --> 1:26:24.471
(rain falling)

1:26:28.893 --> 1:26:31.020
(thunder rumbling)

1:26:37.610 --> 1:26:39.737
HARRY:
Keanu?

1:26:41.780 --> 1:26:43.157
Keanu?

1:26:47.828 --> 1:26:49.246
Keanu?

1:26:50.915 --> 1:26:52.583
Keanu.

1:26:52.666 --> 1:26:54.501
Come on, mate, where are you?

1:26:56.921 --> 1:26:58.839
(groans)

1:27:05.638 --> 1:27:08.474
It's been two nights now
that he's not been here,

1:27:08.557 --> 1:27:11.143
so why the sudden change?

1:27:12.770 --> 1:27:15.356
I hope he's okay.
(clears throat) I hope he's okay.

1:27:21.278 --> 1:27:23.280
(birds chirping)

1:27:31.038 --> 1:27:32.873
Where's he gone?

1:27:33.999 --> 1:27:36.210
♪ ♪

1:27:47.513 --> 1:27:49.264
Keanu.

1:27:53.602 --> 1:27:55.938
Fuck. Fuck.

1:28:02.319 --> 1:28:03.737
(groans)

1:28:07.908 --> 1:28:09.702
Keanu.

1:28:13.414 --> 1:28:15.416
(birds calling)

1:28:17.126 --> 1:28:18.919
(sniffles)

1:28:30.639 --> 1:28:33.017
Hey, Keanu.

1:28:33.100 --> 1:28:34.601
What have you been doing?

1:28:34.685 --> 1:28:36.979
(chuckling):
I've not seen you for five days.

1:28:37.062 --> 1:28:39.064
(Keanu purring)

1:28:39.148 --> 1:28:40.524
This is good, though.

1:28:40.607 --> 1:28:42.985
You spent five days away.

1:28:44.403 --> 1:28:46.071
Mm.

1:28:47.156 --> 1:28:48.991
I'm glad you're okay.

1:29:02.713 --> 1:29:04.882
Oh, it was so nice to see him.

1:29:07.676 --> 1:29:09.344
(sighs)

1:29:14.183 --> 1:29:15.809
(sniffs)

1:29:17.519 --> 1:29:19.688
I feel like I've done something good.

1:29:21.732 --> 1:29:24.526
(crying)

1:29:24.610 --> 1:29:29.073
It's so... it's so stupid that
I'm getting sad about this, but...

1:29:29.156 --> 1:29:30.824
Oh, fuck.

1:29:32.201 --> 1:29:34.203
(crying)

1:29:36.413 --> 1:29:39.208
I feel like I've done something right.

1:29:39.291 --> 1:29:41.293
(continues crying)

1:29:48.092 --> 1:29:50.594
Oh, fucking man up, cunt.

1:29:51.845 --> 1:29:53.472
(sighs)

1:29:54.640 --> 1:29:56.475
(exhales sharply)

1:30:01.021 --> 1:30:02.606
(sniffles)

1:30:06.985 --> 1:30:08.987
(insects trilling)

1:30:09.071 --> 1:30:11.073
♪ ♪

1:30:28.132 --> 1:30:30.467
(insects trilling)

1:30:30.551 --> 1:30:32.302
HARRY:
All right.

1:30:34.304 --> 1:30:36.140
Okay.

1:30:36.223 --> 1:30:37.891
It's recording.

1:30:50.279 --> 1:30:52.114
I'm gonna miss you, man.

1:30:52.197 --> 1:30:53.866
Seriously.

1:30:55.075 --> 1:30:59.580
There won't be a minute...
a minute that goes by

1:30:59.663 --> 1:31:01.999
where I'm not thinking about you.

1:31:03.167 --> 1:31:05.711
(Keanu purring)

1:31:05.794 --> 1:31:07.671
But I need to leave.

1:31:09.673 --> 1:31:11.258
I need to go.

1:31:12.676 --> 1:31:15.345
But maybe I'll see you again.

1:31:15.429 --> 1:31:18.432
But if I don't,
then just know that I love you.

1:31:22.728 --> 1:31:24.646
(crying):
Because I do, man.

1:31:24.730 --> 1:31:27.149
I love you with everything I've got.

1:31:29.693 --> 1:31:31.695
(Keanu purring)

1:31:36.658 --> 1:31:38.452
(chuckles)

1:31:38.535 --> 1:31:40.037
This is lovely.

1:31:40.120 --> 1:31:41.914
Thank you.

1:31:43.415 --> 1:31:45.209
(sniffles)

1:31:45.292 --> 1:31:47.211
(chuckles):
Hey.

1:31:48.670 --> 1:31:51.340
Your teeth are too big for that now,
you little shit.

1:31:52.341 --> 1:31:54.343
♪ ♪

1:32:08.523 --> 1:32:10.525
♪ ♪

1:32:17.866 --> 1:32:19.618
Goodbye, man.

1:32:22.412 --> 1:32:23.622
(sighs)

1:32:33.090 --> 1:32:35.092
♪ ♪

1:32:46.311 --> 1:32:48.146
(grunts)

1:32:52.693 --> 1:32:54.569
(chatter in Spanish)

1:32:54.653 --> 1:32:57.030
HARRY:
What time is it?

1:32:57.114 --> 1:32:59.283
It's time to fucking go home.

1:32:59.366 --> 1:33:01.660
(engine revving)

1:33:05.956 --> 1:33:08.917
(cheering)

1:33:09.001 --> 1:33:10.419
Fuck.

1:33:26.560 --> 1:33:29.730
God, it's fucking cold. (groans)

1:33:32.190 --> 1:33:34.401
I'm not used to this fucking cold.

1:33:34.484 --> 1:33:36.445
All right, I think that's them.

1:33:37.612 --> 1:33:39.364
Yeah, that's them.

1:33:42.242 --> 1:33:44.703
See how surprised they get.

1:33:44.786 --> 1:33:47.164
Hey, you going to Pizza Hut without me?

1:33:47.247 --> 1:33:48.957
-COLETTE: What in the bloody hell?
-(laughter)

1:33:49.041 --> 1:33:51.001
What are you fucking doing here?

1:33:51.084 --> 1:33:52.753
Oh, my God!

1:33:53.879 --> 1:33:55.881
-HARRY: How you doing?
-Guess where we're going.

1:33:55.964 --> 1:33:57.716
-Pizza Hut.
-Yeah, without me.

1:33:57.799 --> 1:33:59.760
You were gonna go without me.

1:33:59.843 --> 1:34:01.428
MARK:
What are you doing here?

1:34:01.511 --> 1:34:03.347
Oh, my God.

1:34:03.430 --> 1:34:05.891
-HARRY: You all right? How you doing?
-MARK: I thought it was next week.

1:34:05.974 --> 1:34:08.185
HARRY:
Yeah, I lied to you. (laughs)

1:34:08.268 --> 1:34:10.228
-HARRY: How you doing, mate?
-MAN: Yeah, sorry, Mark.

1:34:10.312 --> 1:34:12.564
-Don't you ever do that again!
-(laughter)

1:34:12.647 --> 1:34:15.108
(indistinct chatter, laughter)

1:34:17.736 --> 1:34:19.654
HARRY:
You all right, mate?

1:34:21.907 --> 1:34:24.201
(Mark sobbing)

1:34:31.458 --> 1:34:33.460
HARRY:
It's good to see you guys.

1:34:34.461 --> 1:34:36.713
(laughter)

1:34:39.049 --> 1:34:40.926
Yeah.

1:34:41.009 --> 1:34:43.637
(laughter)

1:34:43.720 --> 1:34:45.722
You're lucky you didn't lose
your finger, though.

1:34:52.187 --> 1:34:54.189
♪ ♪

1:35:14.584 --> 1:35:16.586
(sighs heavily)

1:35:28.765 --> 1:35:30.767
♪ ♪

1:35:33.770 --> 1:35:34.855
(bell dings)

1:35:37.190 --> 1:35:39.568
JAYDEN and HARRY:
Three, two, one.

1:35:40.569 --> 1:35:42.446
(laughter)

1:35:42.529 --> 1:35:44.698
(screams, laughs)

1:35:49.077 --> 1:35:51.288
-(laughing): Oh!
-Hey.

1:35:57.294 --> 1:35:58.837
(lawn mower engine shuts off)

1:36:09.723 --> 1:36:12.684
HARRY: But that's why I always
check the edges, you know?

1:36:12.767 --> 1:36:15.228
Don't want to kill one.

1:36:15.312 --> 1:36:19.024
If you just give like extra 15 minutes,
you might be able to save it.

1:36:25.697 --> 1:36:27.699
(birds calling)

1:36:32.787 --> 1:36:34.539
SAMANTHA:
It's still there.

1:36:39.711 --> 1:36:41.338
I've had a lot of time to reflect.

1:36:41.421 --> 1:36:44.341
I definitely realized, you know, like,
I've always been really bad at, like,

1:36:44.424 --> 1:36:46.593
letting people go that aren't good for me.

1:36:49.179 --> 1:36:51.890
And, like, looking back,

1:36:51.973 --> 1:36:56.311
having a dad that was both
verbally and physically abusive,

1:36:56.394 --> 1:36:59.397
and then the next morning,
from 8:00 to 12:00,

1:36:59.481 --> 1:37:02.651
was the nicest, calmest person

1:37:02.734 --> 1:37:05.529
that would reel me back in
by saying, "I'm sorry," and, like,

1:37:05.612 --> 1:37:08.740
really show, like, who he truly was
or who I thought he truly was.

1:37:08.823 --> 1:37:10.659
You know?

1:37:10.742 --> 1:37:14.162
And it's like I replicated that
in my adult life.

1:37:16.289 --> 1:37:18.291
It's a bit heavy.

1:37:20.085 --> 1:37:22.796
After Harry left in December,

1:37:22.879 --> 1:37:26.258
we just, uh, decided
to stop clearing around the house.

1:37:26.341 --> 1:37:28.218
Just to let it all grow.

1:37:28.301 --> 1:37:30.679
Makes sense, you know,
that the jungle eats it.

1:37:31.888 --> 1:37:34.140
Eats the past.

1:37:35.850 --> 1:37:39.062
We have cameras set up all along
this trail and in the front of the house

1:37:39.145 --> 1:37:42.148
to watch for if Keanu comes back
so we can know if we're not here.

1:37:44.276 --> 1:37:46.736
I think there's just, like,
there's so much that's stored

1:37:46.820 --> 1:37:48.947
inside a place like this.

1:37:49.030 --> 1:37:50.657
And I think, on a personal level,

1:37:50.740 --> 1:37:53.994
I just really wanted to have a space
where I could start over.

1:37:54.077 --> 1:37:56.496
♪ ♪

1:38:20.353 --> 1:38:22.480
Aw, that's a good boy.

1:38:27.527 --> 1:38:28.737
(speaking Spanish)

1:38:28.820 --> 1:38:30.155
Is it a boy or a girl?

1:38:30.238 --> 1:38:32.741
-A girl.
-It's a girl.

1:38:33.199 --> 1:38:34.451
My first girl.

1:38:34.534 --> 1:38:35.994
Your first girl.

1:38:46.212 --> 1:38:48.298
SAMANTHA:
You're doing great.

1:38:48.381 --> 1:38:51.343
We named her Kleo, for Cleopatra.

1:38:51.426 --> 1:38:52.594
(laughs)

1:38:52.677 --> 1:38:55.472
Since she's just this powerful
female force already,

1:38:55.555 --> 1:38:57.557
so we thought it was perfect.

1:39:09.819 --> 1:39:13.698
HARRY: As it stands, I'm actually
in a very good place mentally,

1:39:13.782 --> 1:39:17.744
so I feel like now whenever, you know,
I give my family that last hug,

1:39:17.827 --> 1:39:20.997
it's only the last hug for now.

1:39:24.834 --> 1:39:26.503
Holy shit, man.

1:39:26.586 --> 1:39:29.172
I've never seen anything like this.

1:39:30.507 --> 1:39:32.509
It's like I'm in a dream.

1:39:34.511 --> 1:39:37.013
♪ ♪

1:39:40.517 --> 1:39:43.353
I still have negative thoughts,
and I have bad days.

1:39:43.436 --> 1:39:46.064
-WOMAN: Yay!
-MAN: Woo-hoo!

1:39:46.147 --> 1:39:50.735
HARRY: But I have a bad day,
and I think, "Harry, you was happy.

1:39:50.819 --> 1:39:52.612
You can be happy."

1:39:52.696 --> 1:39:55.031
-(indistinct chatter)
-Yay.

1:39:57.701 --> 1:39:59.202
Don't rely on me.

1:39:59.285 --> 1:40:00.578
Just relax. You can do it.

1:40:00.662 --> 1:40:03.665
JAYDEN: I'm already relying on you,
and I feel like I'm going to fall off.

1:40:07.127 --> 1:40:08.336
(Harry laughs)

1:40:09.546 --> 1:40:11.548
(laughter)

1:40:13.007 --> 1:40:15.135
COLETTE:
Oh, lovely.

1:40:15.218 --> 1:40:17.512
Yeah, gorgeous.

1:40:17.595 --> 1:40:19.931
HARRY: But I definitely think about him
every single day.

1:40:20.014 --> 1:40:21.725
(tool buzzing)

1:40:24.018 --> 1:40:28.106
I have hope inside of my heart
that he is out there still,

1:40:28.189 --> 1:40:30.400
he has mated with a female

1:40:30.483 --> 1:40:33.403
and now there's other little Keanus
out there.

1:40:35.447 --> 1:40:40.452
I'm proud to have got him to a point
of where he did eventually go off.

1:40:40.535 --> 1:40:42.954
♪ ♪

